# 路徑處理

- **Always use full absolute paths first** when referencing files or directories
- **Fallback to relative paths** if full path is not available
- If project root full path is unknown, read `.project-root-full-path` file
- Example: `/Users/foo/Desktop/tripvota/typescript-workspace/apps/web/package.json` (full path preferred)
- Fallback: `typescript-workspace/apps/web/package.json` (relative path)
